title: JanSport Pack Review: Broadband
description:
Designed for premium digital functionality, the Broadband JanSport backpack features an internal 17 inch laptop sleeve & 360 degree protection, dual water bottle pockets, 10 inch external tablet pocket, & 
padded oversized accessory/headphone pocket.
